                    <p>Plumbing in commercial office buildings and industrial facilities requires a high level of expertise and the use of high-grade, industrial-strength equipment.</p>
                    <p>Mr. Speedy’s commercial plumbing team has many years of professional experience. We have the very latest equipment, technology and tools. We know how to handle any plumbing issue that can develop in large commercial buildings or industrial facilities.</p>
                    <h5><b>We specialize in commercial service and repair. Our commercial/industrial plumbing services include the following:</b></h5>                                                                                                                  
                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b><a href="#">Hydro Jetting</a></b> :  Remove debris/sludge/tree roots from lines, drains and grease traps;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Sewer, Gas, and Water Lines</b>: Diagnostics, replacement or repair;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Faucets & fixtures</b>: Repair, replace, or install new faucets and fixtures;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Video Camera Inspection</b>: Latest video systems to inspect the lines;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b><a href="#">Water Heaters</a></b>: Repair, Service and Installation of heaters;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Sump Pumps</b>: Sales, repair & installation;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Toilets</b>: Sales, Repair & Installation;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Sloan Valves</b>: Rebuild or replace;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b><a href="#">Garbage Disposals</a></b>: Sales, Installation and Repair;</li>                    
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Leak Detection</b>: Electronic detection devices to locate concealed water or gas leaks;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Backflow Testing</b>: Stay compliant – prevent sewage water from backing up into the drinking water;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Tenant Improvement</b>: New bathrooms, kitchens, water heaters, water closets;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Building Repiping</b>: Repipe one unit, a single floor, or an entire building;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Water and Energy Conservation</b>: reduce your water and power bills with “green” technology and Energy Star appliances;</li>
                    <li><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i> <b>Offices, <a href="#">Retail Stores</a>, Restaurants, High-Rise Buildings, Factories, Warehouses.</b></li>
